    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute daytime tapping practice from Day 29 of a 30-day sleep programme. Day 29 theme: end the battle with sleep. The script works with the exhausting pattern of fighting your own body over rest, blaming it for keeping you awake, fearing nights before they arrive, measuring every bad night as evidence the body has failed. The reframe moves toward cooperation: body and mind wanting the same thing and learning how to reach it together.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how EFT tapping works",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Karate chop",
            "type": "text"
          }
